<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288322>
    dc:description "FIGURES 37 – 39. Autogneta schusteri sp. nov., adults, dorsal aspect: 37, female, legs not illustrated, except for proximal segments of leg I and II; 38, male, legs not illustrated, except for proximal segments of legs I – III; 39, male, detail of posterior of notogaster (specimen flattened, and partially broken). Scale bar = 50." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288322/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

